  "description": "<i>Monstrum</i> is a classic platformer, where the player must defeat a deadly creature hiding in the maze. Reaching the monster level requires finding numerous items and using them in an appropriate place, facing hordes of deadly enemies, such as mummies, knights or bats, several types of traps, including ground and rotating spikes. Appropriate use of the jumping skills, accurate knife throwing and timed stick hitting is the key to the success of the mission.\n",
